PGINVIT : 07-Nov-2024 :  The Company has informed the Exchange that a Board meeting to be held on November 05, 2024 has been re-scheduled. Further, the Company has informed the Exchange that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company will be held on November 07, 2024,  To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended September 30, 2024
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended September 30, 2024
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended Jun 30, 2024 and other business matters
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended March 31, 2024 and other business matters
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended December 31, 2023 and other business matters
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended September 30, 2023 and other business matters

We wish to inform that a meeting of Board of Directors of POWERGRID Unchahar Transmission Limited, the Investment Manager to POWERGRID Infrastructure Investment Trust ( PGInvIT ), is scheduled to be held on Thursday, July 27, 2023, to inter alia consider and approve the following:i. Unaudited Standalone Financial Results and Consolidated Financial Results of PGInvIT for the quarter ended June 30, 2023, subject to limited review by Statutory Auditors of PGInvIT; andii. Declaration of distribution to unitholders of PGInvIT for the quarter ended June 30, 2023.We further wish to inform that the Record Date for the purpose of proposed distribution, if declared, will be Wednesday, August 02, 2023. Further, the trading window for trading & dealing in units of PGInvIT which has been closed from Friday, June 30, 2023 for Designated Persons in terms of the  Policy on Unpublished Price Sensitive information and dealing in units by the parties to PGInvIT , shall remain closed upto Saturday, July 29, 2023 and open on Sunday, July 30, 2023.

We wish to inform that a meeting of Board of Directors of POWERGRID Unchahar Transmission Limited, the Investment Manager to POWERGRID Infrastructure Investment Trust ( PGInvIT ), is scheduled to be held on Thursday, May 25, 2023, to inter alia consider and approve the following:i. Audited Standalone and Consolidated Financial Information of PGInvIT for the financial year ended March 31, 2023, subject to report by Statutory Auditors; andii. Declaration of distribution to unitholders of PGInvIT for the quarter ended March 31, 2023.We further wish to inform that the Record Date for the purpose of proposed distribution, if declared, will be Wednesday, May 31, 2023. Further, the trading window for trading & dealing in units of PGInvIT which has been closed from Friday, March 31, 2023 for Designated Persons in terms of the  Policy on Unpublished Price Sensitive information and dealing in units by the parties to PGInvIT , shall remain closed upto Saturday, May 27, 2023 and open on Sunday, May 28, 2023.
